description: I opened my account with the Tarbert, Harris branch of the Bank of Scotland over a quarter-century ago. It sits at the top of Pier Road in stately prominence.

title: 8 out of 10 Scots medics fear 'associates' pose a risk to patients
description: Around 150 physician associates and ­anaesthesia associates work across the health service in Scotland, a role that requires only two years of training.

title: James Packer to the rescue? Aussie billionaire gains a huge stake in Network 10 as studio struggles to bring in viewers
description: The former Channel Nine supremo - who cut his final ties with the free-to-air TV station in 2008 - snapped up the shares through his company Consolidated Press International Holdings.
